</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=baadan>Baadan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.imahosting.com/sigs/posticon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 590<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/03 2:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5341.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Windblade - What level?</span><hr size=1> It goes up 1 dmg per level till your 56.<br>
<br>
56=50<br>
55=49<br>
54=48<br>
53=57<br>
52=46<br>
51=45<br>
50=44<br>
<br>
So pre-49 you would be better off with a Stonebladed Axe of Dismay.<br>
<br>
BUT WAIT!! <br>
<br>
Stonebladed Axe of Dismay<br>
MAGIC ITEM  <br>
Slot: PRIMARY  <br>
Skill: 2H Slashing  Atk Delay: 44<br>
DMG: 44  <br>
HP: +75  <br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Required</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> level of 51.</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
WT:  3.0    Size: MEDIUM<br>
Class: WAR <br>
Race: ALL<br>
<br>
So by the time you can even equip the SBoAD it's already worse than the Windblade!!<br>
<br>
Conclusion? You'll always be better off with a Windblade than you would with a SBoAD.<br>
<br>
But if you can't afford a Windblade the SBoAD is still a great alternative. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=168211" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.imahosting.com/sigs/baadsignew.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:Verdana;font-size:medium;">{54 Champion} <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=168211" target="top">Baadan</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (Half Elf) &lt;<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/bdragonmawguild" target="top">Dragon Maw</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->&gt;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->{44 Necromancer} <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=115139" target="top">Azumaan</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (Erudite) &lt;<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/bdragonmawguild" target="top">Dragon Maw</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->&gt; </div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=baruchthebarbarianbastard>baruch the barbarian bastard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/24/03 3:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5341.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Windblade</span><hr size=1> The Reaver (40/40) is also a good choice. It's cheaper than SBAoD, and it can be used at any level.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valig